WEBVTT

00:06.440 --> 00:09.422
I didn't know you owned a cottage.

00:11.800 --> 00:15.340
Why did you two never live there?

00:15.360 --> 00:19.184
I visited once,
but I never cared for it.

00:19.200 --> 00:22.182
Anyway, it was your grandfather's.

00:24.360 --> 00:27.194
It was really all very basic.

00:34.800 --> 00:36.951
Goodnight.

00:37.000 --> 00:39.185
Goodnight, dear.

